      <h2>About Us</h2>
      <p>
        Our mission is to ensure the safety and empowerment of women across all communities. This platform provides access to vital information, tools, and contacts for staying safe and taking action.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section id="tips" class="section">
      <h2>Safety Tips</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Always share your location with a trusted friend or family member.</li>
        <li>Avoid isolated areas, especially at night.</li>
        <li>Keep emergency contacts easily accessible.</li>
        <li>Use verified ride-sharing apps with safety features.</li>
        <li>Trust your instincts — if something feels wrong, leave the situation.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="resources" class="section">
